天</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上后，放弃了肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 的新“diss 曲目”。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 在发布新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/father-john-misty-mahashmashana-review-3814237">《Mahashmashana》</a>的同一天<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-surprise-releases-brand-new-album-gnx-listen-in-full-3815187">意外发行了他的新专辑《GNX》</a>后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/father-john-misty">约翰·米斯蒂 (John Misty) 神父</a>分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 的</a>一首 diss 歌曲。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/father-john-misty-mahashmashana-review-3814237">约翰·米斯蒂神父 – 《Mahashmashana》评论：轻轻迷幻</a></strong></li></ul><p>英国时间周五（11 月 22 日）下午 5 点，这位康普顿说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-surprise-releases-brand-new-album-gnx-listen-in-full-3815187">在他的社交媒体页面上发布了该专辑的链接</a>，这张 12 首曲目、时长 44 分钟的专辑现已在所有主要音乐流媒体平台上发布。</p><p>此次下跌恰逢 John Misty 神父的《Mahashmashana》发行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/father-john-misty-reacts-to-kendrick-lamar-dropping-surprise-album-the-same-day-as-him-furiously-scribbling-my-seeming-response-3815216">他昨天在 X 上开玩笑地</a>写道：“不是现在，我正在疯狂地写下我看似的回应”。</p><p>现在，回应以一首新歌的形式在 Instagram 上分享，名为“God&#39;s Trash”。这首歌与 Lamar 最近在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/drake-and-kendrick-lamars-feud-the-full-timeline-3754820">今年夏天广为人知的不和</a>中对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drake">Drake</a>的 diss 歌曲的艺术模仿封面一起发布。 “我在等，”蒂尔曼捕捉到了 Instagram 上的帖子。</p><p>看看下面。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DCsXaXsS9Y2/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" versi